  <div class="comment" id="comment13343691">

    <div id="item13343691" class="body">

      <p>Boy Scouts, 1970s...we never went camping without these or &#39;smores, or both. The best thing was smooshing the banana/chocolate/marshmallow concoction between two graham crackers and then trying to eat it without getting it all over yourself. And usually failing.<br/> I haven&#39;t had one of these since...since...well, I can&#39;t remember the last time. I&#39;m gonna have to break down and rediscover them. Thanks for the memory.</p>

    </div>
